Nevada Update: 12,740 Private QHP, about half paid to date.
Thu, 12/26/2013 - 12:00am
Noteworthy mainly because this is the only case other than Washington State where a breakdown betweenpaidandunpaidenrollments is being given.
Update: As of the 12/23/13 deadline to enroll, 12740 consumers confirmed QHP selections, 6219 have paid. Payment deadline is 12/30/13.
